| Step | Command                | Action                                        |
| ---- | ---------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| 1    | `git fetch origin`     | Download remote updates without merging       |
| 2    | `git pull origin main` | Merge remote changes into your local main     |
| 3    | `git add .`            | Stage any fixed or new files                  |
| 4    | `git commit`           | Record a merge commit (if conflicts occurred) |
| 5    | `git push origin main` | Upload your merged branch back to GitHub      |
